Resource Profile: CH ORF Composition

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-orf/StructureDefinition/ch-orf-composition Version: 3.0.1
Active as of 2025-05-22 Computable Name: ChOrfComposition

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

Profile to specify how the generic elements (e.g. patient, author) and the healthcare domain specific elements must be structured in the Composition as the first entry of the document.

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: CH ORF Document
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Composition/comp-order-referral-form
